a Catedral affords some spectacular views.</p></description><accommodation>1 night(s) in hotels . No single room upgrade available.</accommodation><meals>1 Breakfast(s)</meals></itinerary><itinerary><day1>13</day1><day2>13</day2><destfrom>San José</destfrom><destto></destto><description><p>Today you will say goodbye to the beach paradise of Manuel Antonio and will be transferred back to San Jose. Once you have checked in to your hotel, the remainder of the day is free at your leisure to enjoy the remainder of your time in Costa Rica.</p></description><accommodation>1 night(s) in hotels . No single room upgrade available.</accommodation><meals>1 Breakfast(s)</meals></itinerary><itinerary><day1>14</day1><day2>14</day2><destfrom>Depart San José</destfrom><destto></destto><description><p>Your adventure of a lifetime comes to an end today.  If you have a late flight or have lengthened your stay by adding post tour accommodation you will have more time to explore the sights.</p><p>Today you will be collected from your hotel and transferred to the airport to board your onwards flight.</p> <p>Your adventure of a lifetime comes to an end today.  If you have a late flight or have lengthened your stay by adding post tour accommodation you will have more time to explore the sights.</p></description><meals>1 Breakfast(s)</meals><includedexcursions>Departure Transfer</includedexcursions></itinerary></itineraries></tour>